<TITLE> 7.62% rise in defence budget </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Dhaka, June 09 (bdnews24.com)  Finance adviser AB Mirza Azizul Islam has proposed Tk 6,405 crore for the defence ministry for fiscal 2008-09, which is a 7.62 percent rise from the outlay for the outgoing fiscal year. In fiscal 2007-08, Tk 5,470 crore was proposed for the ministry, which was revised up to Tk 5,951 crore. According to the proposed budget, Tk 5,166 crore will be allocated to the home ministry. The revised amount for the ministry in fiscal 2007-08 was Tk 4,751 crore. bd
